Executive Profile
Arthur J. Radin  Managing Partner, Radin, Glass & Co., LLPAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships80--
Background

		Mr. Arthur J. Radin serves as a Managing Partner of Radin, Glass & Co., LLP. Mr. Radin is in charge of the Radin, Glass & Co's accounting and auditing practice. Besides being an Expert in accounting and auditing, he is a proficient and creative tax professional. He serves as a Partner of Feldman Radin Feinsod & Co. He served as a Member of Feldman Radin & Co., P.C. for twenty years and served as its President. He served with Deloitte & Touche for 18 years, including ... being a partner for 10 years. He is an expert in many areas including retailing, publishing, brokerage firms and litigation support, as well as companies in the manufacturing and service industries. He has been a Director of Repro-Med Systems Inc. since January 2015. He served as a Director of Waterhouse Investor Services Inc. since November, 1987. He has served on the SEC Regulations Committee of the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants as well as a number of the New York State Society committees, including the Retail Committee. He is a Member of the New York and Florida Societies of Certified Public Accountants. Mr. Radin received his Bachelor of Arts degree from Columbia College and a Masters in Business Administration from New York University.Read Full Background




